  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The armies of Rome will be here in a day's time! Fight to the bitter end and make the Germanic tribes proud.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rome In A Day is a throwback to the early 2000s RTS games that we all grew up playing. The year is 100 B.C. nearing the end of the Cimbrian War. You play as a Germanic tribe who just received word from a scout that all of Rome is coming down on your village. You only have a day to prepare, so build as fast as you can; once nightfall comes, all hell breaks loose. Build, improve, and defend yourself from a never ending onslaught of Roman soldiers and battlements. Manage your resources and command a barbarian army of unique troop types, including bears bred for maiming men. Is Tyr on your side? Will Odin write your name in The Hall of The Dead?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Featuring two game modes</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One Long Night: Build for a day and defend all night. In this mode the night is eternal and the onslaught never ends. How long can you survive? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wave of Rome: Build over many days, and each night Rome will descend on your village. Each night grows longer and each wave of Roman soldiers becomes increasingly difficult.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Leaderboards</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight like hell to get to the top of the leaderboards. Fight even harder to stay there. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Mechanics</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place structures near specific resource tiles and upgrade buildings to improve their resource output</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370710/extras/519a6ec7f6f27c8152bbd40c5483cbba.poster.avif?t=1742045805\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370710/extras/519a6ec7f6f27c8152bbd40c5483cbba.webm?t=1742045805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370710/extras/519a6ec7f6f27c8152bbd40c5483cbba.mp4?t=1742045805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Generate armies while managing your resources, place soldiers to defend key positions and build defensive structures</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370710/extras/bd16efb92863e1d41efbc3b5251d3ec9.poster.avif?t=1742045805\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370710/extras/bd16efb92863e1d41efbc3b5251d3ec9.webm?t=1742045805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370710/extras/bd16efb92863e1d41efbc3b5251d3ec9.mp4?t=1742045805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Send in the troops!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370710/extras/b77533a09dff65499a57594469593772.poster.avif?t=1742045805\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370710/extras/b77533a09dff65499a57594469593772.webm?t=1742045805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370710/extras/b77533a09dff65499a57594469593772.mp4?t=1742045805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
